      "id": "overview",
      "title": "Role Overview",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "TPM interviews assess your ability to drive complex, cross-functional technical programs. You need to demonstrate technical depth, organizational skills, and the ability to influence without direct authority."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**What interviewers assess:**\n\n- Program management and execution\n- Technical understanding and credibility\n- Stakeholder management and communication\n- Risk identification and mitigation\n- Problem-solving under ambiguity"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "format",
      "title": "Common Interview Format",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**Typical TPM interview loop:**\n\n1. **Recruiter screen** (30 min)\n2. **Hiring manager screen** (60 min)\n3. **Onsite/Virtual loop** (4-5 hours):\n   - Program management scenario round\n   - Technical depth round\n   - Stakeholder management round\n   - Behavioral/leadership round"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "content": {
            "text": "Be ready to walk through a complex program you managed end-to-end. Include timeline, dependencies, risks, stakeholders, and how you tracked progress."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
